header.name: Mountain Abbey of Terror
header.author: BSP-Dungeon-Generator
header.description: The abbey is situated deep in the salt marshes, protected by the dangerous local fauna and impassable terrain. These days it is overrun with bears.

game_elements.name: Item 1
game_elements.description: A rear entrance into the abbey.

game_elements.name: Item 2
game_elements.description: A potion of resistence among rubble on the ground.

game_elements.name: Item 3
game_elements.description: An ogre. Pleads to borrow candles.

game_elements.name: Item 4
game_elements.description: A great door with a keyhole on the southern wall.

game_elements.name: Item 5
game_elements.description: A chest holds a palm-shaped key.

game_elements.name: Item 6
game_elements.description: A staff of power hovering in the middle of the hall.

game_elements.name: Item 7
game_elements.description: A bottomless pit, sounds the alarm if a coin is dropped into it.

game_elements.name: Item 9
game_elements.description: A wall panel conceals a shield and some gold.

game_elements.name: Item 10
game_elements.description: A carving on the wall, totally destroyed by ogre vandals.

game_elements.name: Item 11
game_elements.description: A monk, sleeping in a corner.

game_elements.name: Item 12
game_elements.description: A writing on the floor: DEATH TO OGRES
